en vil avgj\u00f8re om saken skal fremmes."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8104f073034c077dbaf38a6eafcb6583d76fe0f8bb655b9838b0a7020b6ad101"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-11-18T09:52:38.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Meraker Brugs advokat tilbakeviser kravene fra g\u00e5rdbrukerne."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/nordtrondelag/article10106688.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/FC_Meraaker_Brug_rettssak12.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5996e4bef4ea77d0020c9f3e73b5d869d6261a56.jpg?5982c36a"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Avviser jord-kravet -adressa.no", "Ikke fornuftig tvil", "Lang forhistorie", "Kan stoppe saken"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "5996e4bef4ea77d0020c9f3e73b5d869d6261a56"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "meraker brug as"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["eid", "g\u00e5rdbrukere", "million m\u00e5l", "saken", "krav", "fornuftig tvil"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["frostating", "bj\u00f8rn strid og anne lise magnusson", "meraker brug", "hovstads", "mer\u00e5kergodset"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["anne lise magnusson", "bj\u00f8rn strid", "ola oldren", "bj\u00f8rn hovstad", "tore \u00f8ien"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value